<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>135</hymn_number>
<title>THERE IS POWER IN THE BLOOD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na gitloh puokgika pawt na nuom em?
 Thisan, hatna um, thisan hatna;
 Gitloh chunga guolzo hih na nuom em?
 Thisan ah hatna mak a um.

[V2]
 Hatna a..... um, hatna nasep mak,
 Belam No thisan ah;
 Hatna a.... um, hatna nasep mak,
 Belam No....thisan lul achun.

[V3]
 2. Kideih, lungnat apat pawt na nuom em?
 Thisan hatna um, thisan hatna;
 Kalvari tuiphul ah thieng di'n hungin,
 Thisan ah hatna mak a um.

[V4]
 3. Vuk sangin hahpin vamzawk na nuom em?
 Thisan hatna um, thisan hatna;
 Thisan luong chun gitlohna a sawp thieng,
 Thisan ah hatna mak a um.

[V5]
 4. Na Lalpen Isu na chuh na sem dem?
 Thisan hatna um, thisan hatna;
 Nicheng in A pahchakla na sa dem?
 Thisan ah hatna mak a um.</lyrics>
</song>